    Add periodic GRF-to-SDF pipeline for metamaterial unit-cell generation
    
    Implements Step 1 of the inverse design data-generation pipeline,
    aligned with Liu et al. (CMAME 2025) / SDFGeoDesign reference:
    - Periodic GRF via gstools Fourier generator (var=10, len_scale=0.15, mode_no=32)
    - Adaptive thresholding relative to field range
    - Shapely-based exact SDF with GRF interpolation for sign determination
    - Validation filters: periodic connectivity, small hole removal,
      narrow region detection, boundary proximity rejection
    - Batch generation with visualization (SDF gallery, GRF gallery, detail view)

